<doc id="198707" wikidata="Q1819536" url="?curid=198707" title="List of people on the postage stamps of the Netherlands">
<text>This article lists people who have been featured on the postage stamps of the Netherlands. Note that many of these people have been featured on multiple stamps. The following entries list the name of the person, a short description of their notability, and the first year they were first featured on a stamp.

This list is complete up to 2021.

==A==
*Afrojack, disk jockey (2014)
*Princess Alexia of the Netherlands, second daughter of King Willem-Alexander (2012)
*Princess Ariane of the Netherlands, third daughter of King Willem-Alexander (2012)
*Anthony van Assche, gymnast (2009)
*Tobias Michael Carel Asser, jurist and Nobel prize winner (1991)

==B==
*Willem Barents, explorer (1996)
