*&quot;Nu-Clear Sounds&quot; (1998)
*&quot;Free All Angels&quot; (2001)
*&quot;Meltdown&quot; (2004)
*&quot;Twilight of the Innocents&quot; (2007)
*&quot;Kablammo!&quot; (2015)
*&quot;Islands&quot; (2018)
*&quot;Race the Night&quot; (2023)

